{"title_page": "Amber Midthunder", "text_new": "{{Use mdy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{short description|American actress}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Amber Midthunder\n| image              = Amber Midthunder - 2019 (46801505974) (cropped).jpg\n| caption            = Midthunder in 2019\n| occupation         = Actress\n| years_active       = 2001\u2013present\n}}\n\n'''Amber Midthunder''' is an American actress. She is known for her main role in the FX series ''[[Legion (TV series)|Legion]]'', and appearances in ''[[Longmire (TV series)|Longmire]]'' and ''[[Banshee (TV series)|Banshee]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/legion-amber-midthunder-cast-fx-marvel-pilot-1201707006/|title=\u2018Legion\u2019 FX Pilot Casts Amber Midthunder|author=Nellie Andreeva|website=Deadline|date=February 22, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://tworowtimes.com/arts-and-culture/amber-midthunders-blossoming-career-marvel-studios/|title=Amber Midthunder\u2019s blossoming career with Marvel Studios|author=Benjamin II|website=tworowtimes|date=March 1, 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Biography==\nHer father, David Midthunder, is an actor and her mother is a casting director.{{cn|date=October 2019}} Amber is [[Native Americans in the United States|Native American]] and an enrolled member of the [[Fort Peck Indian Reservation|Fort Peck Sioux Tribe]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://indiancountrymedianetwork.com/culture/arts-entertainment/amber-midthunder-kicks-butt-native-woman-superhero-fx-networks-legion/|title=Amber Midthunder Kicks Butt as a Native Woman Superhero on FX Network's 'Legion' |work=Indian Country Media Network|language=en-US|access-date=November 20, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.powwows.com/amber-midthunder-x-men-tv-pilot-legion/|title=Amber Midthunder in X-Men TV Pilot \"Legion\" - PowWows.com - Native American Pow Wows|date=February 25, 2016|work=PowWows.com - Native American Pow Wows|access-date=November 20, 2017|language=en-US}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n\n===Film===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n|2001\n|''{{sortname|The|Homecoming of Jimmy Whitecloud|nolink=1}}''\n|Little Girl\n|\n|-\n|2002\n|''Deadly Species''\n|Calusa Tribe\n|Direct-to-video film\n|-\n|2008\n|''[[Sunshine Cleaning]]''\n|Candy Store Girl\n|\n|-\n|2008\n|''[[Swing Vote (2008 film)|Swing Vote]]''\n|Female Student #3\n|\n|-\n|2009\n|''[[Not Forgotten (film)|Not Forgotten]]''\n|Amaya Bishop (young)\n|\n|-\n|2014\n|''[[Drunktown's Finest]]''\n|Model #1\n|\n|-\n|2015\n|''[[Spare Parts (2015 film)|Spare Parts]]''\n|Nikki\n|\n|-\n|2015\n|''[[Bare (film)|Bare]]''\n|Malya\n|\n|-\n|2016\n|''[[Hell or High Water (2016 film)|Hell or High Water]]''\n|Vernon Teller\n|\n|-\n|2016\n|''[[Priceless (2016 film)|Priceless]]''\n|Maria\n|\n|-\n|2018\n|''14 Cameras''\n|Danielle\n|\n|-\n|2018\n|''[[She's Missing]]''\n|Honey\n|\n|-\n|2019\n|''Only Mine''\n|Julie Dillon\n|Direct-to-video film\n|-\n|2020\n|''Centurion the Dancing Stallion''\n|Elissa Hall\n|Upcoming film<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/amber-midthunder-cast-centurion-dancing-stallion-1213530|title=Amber Midthunder Grabs Lead in Drama 'Centurion the Dancing Stallion' (Exclusive)|website=The Hollywood Reporter|language=en|access-date=May 28, 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n|2012\u20132014\n|''[[Longmire (TV series)|Longmire]]''\n|Lilly Stillwater\n|Episodes: \"Pilot\", \"Miss Cheyenne\"\n|-\n|2014\n|''[[Banshee (TV series)|Banshee]]''\n|Lana Cleary\n|Episodes: \"The Warrior Class\", \"Bloodlines\"\n|-\n|2015\n|''[[Dig (TV series)|Dig]]''\n|Starlet\n|Episode: \"Emma Watson's Father\"\n|-\n|2016\n|''{{sortname|The|Originals|The Originals (TV series)}}''\n|Kayla\n|Episode: \"Alone with Everybody\"\n|-\n|2017\u20132019\n|''[[Legion (TV series)|Legion]]''\n|Kerry Loudermilk\n|Main role\n|-\n|2018\n|''{{sortname|The|Mi