crease}} || 11th || \u2014 || 33,703 || {{decrease}}\n|-\n| 2014 || 54,249 || {{increase}} || 10th || \u2014 || 48,046 || {{increase}}\n|-\n| 2015 || 52,920 || {{decrease}} || 7th || 6th || 46,487 || {{decrease}}\n|-\n| 2016 || 54,307 || {{increase}} || 5th || 6th || 47,056 || {{increase}}\n|-\n| 2017 || 56,865 || {{increase}} || 1st || Runners-up || 47,675 || {{increase}} || 2nd || '''Premiers''' || 8,876 || {{N/A}}\n|-\n| 2018 || 64,739 || {{increase}} || 12th || \u2014 || 45,417 || {{decrease}} || 5th || \u2014 || 6,037 || {{decrease}}\n|-\n| 2019 || 64,437 || {{decrease}} || 11th\n|  || || || 1st A || '''Premiers''' || 14,698 || {{increase}}\n|}\n\n==Club honour board==\n\n===Club achievements===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#bdb76b;\" align=\"center\"| '''Premierships'''\n|- style=\"background:#bdb76b;\"\n!Competition\n!Level\n!Wins\n!Years Won\n|-\n|'''[[Australian Football League|AFL]]'''||Seniors||2|| [[1997 AFL Grand Final|1997]], [[1998 AFL Grand Final|1998]]\n|-\n|'''[[AFL Women's]]'''||Seniors||2|||[[2017 AFL Women's Grand Final|2017]], [[2019 AFL Women's Grand Final|2019]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#bdb76b;\" align=\"center\"| '''Other titles and honours'''\n|-\n|'''[[Australian Football League|AFL]]'''||[[Australian Football League pre-season competition|Preseason premiership]]||2|| [[2003 Wizard Home Loans Cup|2003]], [[2012 NAB Cup|2012]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#bdb76b;\" align=\"center\"| '''Finishing positions'''\n|-\n||'''[[Australian Football League|VFL/AFL]]'''||[[List of Australian Football League minor premiers|Minor premiership]]||2||[[2005 AFL season|2005]], [[2017 AFL season|2017]] \n|-\n||'''[[Australian Football League|VFL/AFL]]'''||Runners-up||1|| [[2017 AFL Grand Final|2017]]\n|-\n||'''[[Australian Football League|VFL/AFL]]'''||[[Wooden spoon (award)|Wooden Spoons]]||0||\n|}\n\n===Records===\n* '''''Highest score for:''''' 30.8 (188) \u2013 vs {{AFL Ess}} at [[AAMI Stadium|Football Park]] on 2 June 2006 (Round 10)\n* '''''Lowest score for:''''' 3.6 (24) \u2013 vs {{AFL StK}} at [[Docklands Stadium|Etihad Stadium]] on 22 July 2011 (Round 18)\n* '''''Highest score against:''''' 32.18 (210) \u2013 {{AFL Gee}} at [[Kardinia Park]] on 9 May 1992 (Round 8)\n* '''''Lowest score against:''''' 1.7 (13) \u2013 {{AFL Fre}} at [[AAMI Stadium|Football Park]] on 11 July 2009 (Round 15)\n* '''''Highest aggregate score:''''' 44.33 (297) \u2013 vs {{AFL Gee}} at [[Kardinia Park]] on 9 May 1992 (Round 8)\n* '''''Lowest aggregate score:''''' 11.19 (85) \u2013 vs {{AFL Mel}} at [[Melbourne Cricket Ground|the MCG]] on 26 April 2009 (Round 5)\n* '''''Lowest winning score:''''' 6.12 (48) \u2013 vs {{AFL Col}} at [[Football Park]] on 25 August 1997 (Round 21)\n* '''''Highest losing score:''''' 19.11 (125) \u2013 vs {{AFL Kan}} at [[Football Park]] on 6 May 2000 (Round 9)\n* '''''Highest quarter score:''''' 14.2 (86) \u2013 vs {{AFL Fit}} at [[Football Park]] on 28 July 1996 (Round 17, second quarter)\n* '''''Greatest winning margin''''': 139 points \u2013 vs {{AFL Ric}} at [[Football Park]] on 16 July 1993 (Round 16)\n* '''''Greatest losing margin''''': 141 points \u2013 vs {{AFL Bri}} at [[the Gabba]] on 24 July 2004 (Round 17)\n* '''''Longest winning streak:''''' 10 matches \u2013 from 18 June 2005 (Round 13, vs {{AFL Ric}} at [[Telstra Dome]]) to 27 August 2005 (Round 22, vs {{AFL WC}} at [[Subiaco Oval]])\n* '''''Longest losing streak:''''' 9 matches \u2013 from 8 August 1999 (Round 19, vs {{AFL Bri}} at [[Football Park]]) to 8 April 2000 (Round 5, vs {{AFL Bri}} at [[the Gabba]])\n* '''''Longest winning streak against an opponent:''''' 11 matches \u2013 vs {{AFL GC}} from 14 May 2011 (Round 8, at [[Football Park]]) to 28 April 2018 (Round 6, at [[Adelaide Oval]]; streak ongoing)\n* '''''Longest losing streak against an opponent:''''' 7 matches \u2013 vs {{AFL PA}} from 6 August 2000 (Round 22, at [[Football Park]]) to 31 August 2003 (Round 22, at [[Football Park]]), vs {{AFL Haw}} from 15 April 2012 (Round 3, at the [[Melbourne Cricket Ground|MCG]]) to 22 April 2016 (Round 5, at the [[MCG]])\n* '''''Largest home attendance:''''' 53,817 \u2013 vs {{AFL Gee}} at the [[Adelaide Oval]] on 22 September 2017 (Preliminary Final)\n* '''''Largest non-finals attendance:''''' 54,790 \u2013 vs {{AFL Col}} at [[Melbourne Cricket Ground|the MCG]] on 12 July 2013 (Round 16)\n* '''''Largest attendance:''''' 100,021 \u2013 vs [[Richmond Football Club|Richmond]] at the [[Melbourne Cricket Ground|MCG]] on 30 September 2017 ([[2017 AFL Grand Final|Grand Final]])\n* '''''Most goals in a match by an individual:''''' 13 \u2013 [[Tony Modra]] vs {{AFL Ric}} at [[Football Park]] on 16 July 1993 (Round 16), [[Tony Modra]] vs {{AFL Car}} at [[Football Park]] on 27 March 1994 (Round 1)\n* '''''Most disposals in a match by an individual:''''' 51 \u2013 [[Scott Thompson (footballer born 1983)|Scott Thompson]] vs {{AFL GC}} at [[Metricon Stadium]] on 20 August 2011 (Round 22)\n\n===AFL finishing positions (1991\u2013present)===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#bdb76b;\"\n! Finishing Position !! Year ([[AFL finals series|Finals]] in Bold)!!Tally\n|-\n|Premiers||'''1997''', '''1998'''||'''2'''\n|-\n|Runner Up||'''2017'''||'''1'''\n|-\n|3rd||'''1993''', '''2005''', '''2006''', '''2012'''||'''4'''\n|-\n|4th||'''2002'''||'''1'''\n|-\n|5th||'''2003''', '''2009'''||'''2'''\n|-\n|6th||'''2015''', '''2016'''||'''2'''\n|-\n|7th||'''2008'''||'''1'''\n|-\n|8th||'''2001''', '''2007'''||'''2'''\n|-\n|9th||1991, 1992||'''2'''\n|-\n|10th||2014||'''1'''\n|-\n|11th||1994, 1995, 2000, 2010, 2013, 2019||'''6'''\n|-\n|12th||1996, 2004, 2018||'''3'''\n|-\n|13th||1999||'''1'''\n|-\n|14th||2011||'''1'''\n|-\n|15th||nil||'''0'''\n|-\n|16th||nil||'''0'''\n|-\n|17th||nil||'''0'''\n|-\n|18th|| nil||'''0'''\n|}\n\n===Premierships===\n{{AFLGameDetailed\n|title        = [[1997 AFL Grand Final]]\n|date         = Saturday, 27 September (2:30&nbsp;pm)\n|home te