ball Club|Richmond]] at the [[Melbourne Cricket Ground|MCG]] on 30 September 2017 ([[2017 AFL Grand Final|Grand Final]])\n* '''''Most goals in a match by an individual:''''' 13 \u2013 [[Tony Modra]] vs {{AFL Ric}} at [[Football Park]] on 16 July 1993 (Round 16), [[Tony Modra]] vs {{AFL Car}} at [[Football Park]] on 27 March 1994 (Round 1)\n* '''''Most disposals in a match by an individual:''''' 51 \u2013 [[Scott Thompson (footballer born 1983)|Scott Thompson]] vs {{AFL GC}} at [[Metricon Stadium]] on 20 August 2011 (Round 22)\n\n===AFL finishing positions (1991\u2013present)===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#bdb76b;\"\n! Finishing Position !! Year ([[AFL finals series|Finals]] in Bold)!!Tally\n|-\n|Premiers||'''1997''', '''1998'''||'''2'''\n|-\n|Runner Up||'''2017'''||'''1'''\n|-\n|3rd||'''1993''', '''2005''', '''2006''', '''2012'''||'''4'''\n|-\n|4th||'''2002'''||'''1'''\n|-\n|5th||'''2003''', '''2009'''||'''2'''\n|-\n|6th||'''2015''', '''2016'''||'''2'''\n|-\n|7th||'''2008'''||'''1'''\n|-\n|8th||'''2001''', '''2007'''||'''2'''\n|-\n|9th||1991, 1992||'''2'''\n|-\n|10th||2014||'''1'''\n|-\n|11th||1994, 1995, 2000, 2010, 2013, 2019||'''6'''\n|-\n|12th||1996, 2004, 2018||'''3'''\n|-\n|13th||1999||'''1'''\n|-\n|14th||2011||'''1'''\n|-\n|15th||nil||'''0'''\n|-\n|16th||nil||'''0'''\n|-\n|17th||nil||'''0'''\n|-\n|18th|| nil||'''0'''\n|}\n\n===Premierships===\n{{AFLGameDetailed\n|title        = [[1997 AFL Grand Final]]\n|date         = Saturday, 27 September (2:30&nbsp;pm)\n|home team    = {{AFL StK}}\n|home Q1      = 3.6 (24)\n|home Q2      = 7.11 (53)\n|home Q3      = 9.13 (67)\n|home final   = 13.16 (94)\n|home ET      = \n|home goals   = [[Jason Heatley|Heatley]] 3, [[Barry Hall|Hall]] 3, [[Stewart Loewe|Loewe]] 2, [[Austinn Jones|Jones]], [[Nathan Burke|Burke]], [[Nicky Winmar|Winmar]], [[Justin Peckett|Peckett]], [[Robert Harvey (footballer)|Harvey]]\n|home best    =  [[Robert Harvey (footballer)|Harvey]], [[Austinn Jones|Jones]], [[Nathan Burke|Burk